ial for higher efficiencies through lower\nfront grid shadowing factors, as demonstrated with the concentrator\nmeasurements presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Nov 2019 16:41:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-27"}
