s. Our evaluation results show\nthat one defense can effectively defend against our attacks in some cases, but\nthe defenses are not effective enough in other cases, highlighting the need for\nnew defenses against our local model poisoning attacks to federated learning.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Nov 2019 20:10:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Apr 2020 20:59:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 02:15:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 21 Nov 2021 19:04:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-23"}
