 DL based\nencrypted traffic classifier over dataset augmented by PacketCGAN can achieve\nbetter performance than the others.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Nov 2019 09:46:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-28"}
