ease in vaccination coverage. Those results\nsupport the potential utility of further extending the levels of influenza\nvaccination, the use of quadrivalent influenza vaccines, and extra efforts for\nprotecting individuals with circulatory disease in Russia, including\nvaccination and the use of antiviral medications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Nov 2019 10:31:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-28"}
