ypes of medium expansion point\nto the importance of the medium expansion for precise modeling of the jet\nquenching phenomenon.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Nov 2019 14:52:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Jan 2020 11:30:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2020 08:56:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-24"}
